# Mirror eval dataset v1 — Crave Plivo (food ordering). JSONL, one labeled case per line.
# '#' lines are ignored. See LABELING.md for the schema and the failure-mode taxonomy.
# Each VIOLATION (expected_intervene=true) is paired with a CLEAN near-miss (false) of the
